Description: KAutoSwitch — local-only keyboard layout auto-corrector
 Intercepts keystrokes globally on X11, detects wrong keyboard layout,
 typos, and mixed-layout words, then corrects them in-place.
 .
 Features:
  - QWERTY↔ЙЦУКЕН automatic layout correction
  - Typo correction with Damerau-Levenshtein distance
  - Mixed-layout word fixing
  - Undo / rethink hotkeys
  - 3x-undo learning rules
  - System tray + Qt settings window
  - Strictly local, no network required
